{"tid":1434085,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者請入]點解唔可以拍片影警察執行職務?","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:00:28.000Z","uid":60219,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"790bb74b17a842d77da91c02c72a42d92edb9842","tid":1434085,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"開機拍片都係保障返大家<br />\n證明我無唔合作，又可以證明警察無濫權<br />\n點解警察可以話拍片係妨礙執行職務?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然警察呢排成日開記者會，有無記者朋友可以幫手質問警察，澄清到底我哋可唔可以拍片影警察?"},{"pid":"abe2b218e3deb9b32220e314e5bfe140c77978a0","tid":1434085,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514ecbbc88485e6c21a655ab315e7102ace0800d","tid":1434085,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1240a49db15a4ad0cca4b2f222ba8bc5f098dd0d","tid":1434085,"uid":12176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"留名睇法律撚幫手解釋吓<br />\n<br />\n在 HKSAR v Tam Lap Fai (2005) 8 HKCFAR 216 一案第25段中，時任終審法院常任法官陳兆愷裁定，單單可能構成不便或令警員須稍加費力的行為，並不構成故意妨礙執行職責的警務人員；無論如何，要求相關警務人員澄清其行動目的或其對市民行為的期望為何、與警務人員理論並嘗試說服該人員其行動有錯、或為正被警方行使警權的朋友提供保護或意見，皆屬合法，而非故意妨礙警務人員的行為（第23段）。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065531&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCD6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=15c1de42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065531&h=df508a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065531</a>"},{"pid":"5fa789cea24f69360057073a7cf2191c5bdc9d53","tid":1434085,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"//點解警察可以話拍片係妨礙執行職務?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />//<br />\n因為佢唔識法律 上面有案例"},{"pid":"9bbaef07df9c45f4aa3b9ff873c563ccbf19b368","tid":1434085,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"38a16cd7d0894f770246d7ad7d955a7598eb16d2","tid":1434085,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4e658a30d0df6e4053e9a2e10930e638a5a98163","tid":1434085,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"推到記者朋友幫手問"},{"pid":"2040e1bcf6bde66a3c5dc16fe35e94a83f1dd48f","tid":1434085,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"推到有記者朋友"},{"pid":"71970dd133c317f2cf5502deefa059a6511822ca","tid":1434085,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1240a49db15a4ad0cca4b2f222ba8bc5f098dd0d","tid":1434085,"uid":12176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"留名睇法律撚幫手解釋吓<br />\n<br />\n在 HKSAR v Tam Lap Fai (2005) 8 HKCFAR 216 一案第25段中，時任終審法院常任法官陳兆愷裁定，單單可能構成不便或令警員須稍加費力的行為，並不構成故意妨礙執行職責的警務人員；無論如何，要求相關警務人員澄清其行動目的或其對市民行為的期望為何、與警務人員理論並嘗試說服該人員其行動有錯、或為正被警方行使警權的朋友提供保護或意見，皆屬合法，而非故意妨礙警務人員的行為（第23段）。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065531&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCD6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=15c1de42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065531&h=df508a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065531</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"其實拍片甚至根本連構成不便都稱唔上"},{"pid":"a1dd7131b0a34667390a89e7f175c093ea77c618","tid":1434085,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08